### Obtener todos los characters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/characters

### Obtener un character por id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/character/1

### Crear un character
POST http://localhost:3000/api/character
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Aragorn",
    "nickname": "Strider",
    "class_name": "Ranger",
    "race": "Human",
    "level": 20,
    "experience_points": 50000,
    "health_points": 150,
    "mana_points": 80,
    "strength": 18,
    "agility": 16,
    "intelligence": 14,
    "defense": 15,
    "is_alive": true,
    "avatar_url": "https://example.com/aragorn.jpg",
    "backstory": "Heir of Isildur and rightful King of Gondor"
}

### Actualizar un character
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/character/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "level": 21,
    "experience_points": 55000,
    "health_points": 160
}

### Eliminar un character
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/character/1
